    "raw_ingredients": "Alcohol Denat., Butane, Isobutane, Propane, Parfum, Zinc Neodecanoate, Isopropyl Myristate, Benzyl Alcohol, Benzyl Benzoate, Beta-Caryophyllene, Camphor, Carvone, Citral, Citronellol, Citrus Aurantium Peel Oil, Citrus Limon Peel Oil, Coumarin, Eugenol, Geraniol, Geranyl Acetate, Juniperus Virginiana Oil, Limonene, Linalool, Linalyl Acetate, Menthol, Pinene, Pogostemon Cablin Oil, Tetramethyl Acetyloctahydronaphthalenes, Vanillin.",
